430
00:32:05,982 --> 00:32:06,984
什么意思？
What does that mean?

431
00:32:07,076 --> 00:32:10,540
我也不清楚 我让Rat把Juice和他的车接回来
I don't know, but we just sent
Rat to pick up Juice and his bike.

432
00:32:11,114 --> 00:32:13,151
