High?

442
00:32:32,917 --> 00:32:34,456
呃 是病了
Uh, sick.

443
00:32:35,665 --> 00:32:39,123
不 你去看看Wendy 我得去探望Clay
No, you got to go check on Wendy.I got to go see Clay.

444
00:32:39,199 --> 00:32:41,840
