00:34:09,938 --> 00:34:11,429
我不知道有人在
I didn't know anyone was here.

458
00:34:15,420 --> 00:34:16,827
你想要干嘛？
What do you want?

459
00:34:18,129 --> 00:34:20,739
顺便路过 拿些孩子们的东西
Coming by to get some of the boys' things.

460
00:34:21,659 --> 00:34:24,756
要是他们到奶奶家过一段时间 也许能用上
Just in case they need to spend some time at Grandma's.

461
00:34:25,077 --> 00:34:26,780
是吧 那是不可能的
Yeah, that's not gonna happen.

462
00:34:27,182 --> 00:34:28,574
真的吗？
Really?

463
00:34:30,967 --> 00:34:35,149
那你认为会怎样 Tara？
And what is it you think is going to happen, Tara?

464
00:34:39,823 --> 00:34:43,112
你知道为什么你那么讨厌我所做的一切
You know why you hate what I did so much?

465
00:34:44,699 --> 00:34:46,911
因为这些事情你应该做到的
Because it's something you would've done.

466
00:34:48,547 --> 00:34:51,948
你一直是我的师傅 Gemma 
You've been my teacher, Gemma, my...


467
00:34:52,414 --> 00:34:56,034
我的教练 自从我回到Charming镇以后
old lady coach since I came back to Charming.

468
00:34:56,146 --> 00:34:58,111
