Your bridges are all burning, Mom.

480
00:35:37,376 --> 00:35:40,197
我认为你最好多交点朋友
I'd think you'd be trying to make as many friends as possible.

481
00:35:40,289 --> 00:35:43,007
我不需要朋友 我有我的家人
I don't need friends. I have my family.

482
00:35:43,646 --> 00:35:46,397
你真的相信这个 对吗？
You honestly believe that, don't you?

483
00:35:51,993 --> 00:35:54,153
你是怎么想的 这样做能成功？
How'd you think this was gonna play out?

484
00:35:54,792 --> 00:35:58,298
假如发生最好的情形 你的计划成功了
Best case scenario,your plan worked.

485
00:35:58,481 --> 00:36:03,618
你和Jax离婚 不管是你还是Wendy 把孩子带到
You divorce Jax, either you or
Wendy take those boys on up to

486
00:36:03,745 --> 00:36:06,212
俄勒冈州或其他什么地方
Oregon or wherever.

487
00:36:08,208 --> 00:36:11,775
你真的以为Jax会让这一切发生吗？
Did you really think Jax was gonna let that happen?

488
00:36:11,875 --> 00:36:13,819
他别无选择
He'd have no choice.

489
00:36:14,762 --> 00:36:18,716
