All you can do now is tell him you're sorry and go away.

499
00:36:59,973 --> 00:37:02,323
我绝不会这样做
I'll never do that.

500
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:05,767
我绝不放弃我的孩子
Not without my sons.

501
00:37:07,542 --> 00:37:09,656
