I'll give you Gaalan O'Shay within the next 48 hours.

524
00:39:04,268 --> 00:39:06,267
能说详细一点吗？
Can you be a little more specific?

525
00:39:06,586 --> 00:39:09,992
明天我去找你 把所有细节都告诉你
I'll meet you tomorrow, give you all the details.

526
00:39:11,362 --> 00:39:13,402
